                      "name": "intro",
                      "fill": "#785E48",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Crucis is an autonomy scaffold for code-generating agents. It provides structured automated feedback — tests, adversarial review, constraints, holdout verification — so agents can iterate longer without human intervention. The result: generated code that actually works beyond the examples you gave it.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.6,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
