                        {
                          "type": "frame",
                          "id": "7wxYC",
                          "name": "subAgentBinary",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "layout": "vertical",
                          "gap": 8,
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "pssr2",
                              "name": "sub3h3",
                              "fill": "#2D1F14",
                              "content": "Agent binary not found",
                              "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
                              "fontSize": 18,
                              "fontWeight": "600"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "frame",
                              "id": "lSML2",
                              "name": "codeBlock5",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "fill": "#231A12",
                              "cornerRadius": 10,
                              "padding": [
                                16,
                                20
                              ],
                              "children": [
                                {
                                  "type": "text",
                                  "id": "4SlTK",
                                  "name": "sub3codeText",
                                  "fill": "#e8e6e3",
                                  "content": "Error: claude binary not found on PATH",
                                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                                  "fontFamily": "JetBrains Mono",
                                  "fontSize": 12.5,
                                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                                }
                              ]
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "qQrJq",
                              "name": "sub3p",
                              "fill": "#785E48",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "Crucis runs agents as CLI subprocesses. Ensure the agent binary is installed and on your PATH:",
                              "lineHeight": 1.6,
                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                              "fontSize": 14,
                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "frame",
                              "id": "5M0Ln",
                              "name": "codeBlock6",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "fill": "#231A12",
                              "cornerRadius": 10,
                              "padding": [
                                16,
                                20
                              ],
                              "children": [
                                {
                                  "type": "text",
                                  "id": "QoJgO",
                                  "name": "sub3fixText",
                                  "fill": "#e8e6e3",
                                  "content": "which claude\nwhich codex",
                                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                                  "fontFamily": "JetBrains Mono",
                                  "fontSize": 12.5,
                                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                                }
                              ]
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "CPqc6",
                              "name": "sub3note",
                              "fill": "#785E48",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "If the binary is missing, install the relevant CLI tool. The agent returns exit_code=-1 when the binary is not found, and Crucis retries with the next iteration.\n\nRun diagnostics to verify binaries and environment quickly:",
                              "lineHeight": 1.6,
                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                              "fontSize": 14,
                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "frame",
                              "id": "1MZvF",
                              "name": "codeBlock6b",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "fill": "#231A12",
                              "cornerRadius": 10,
                              "padding": [
                                16,
                                20
                              ],
                              "children": [
                                {
                                  "type": "text",
                                  "id": "l3EWr",
                                  "name": "sub3doctorText",
                                  "fill": "#e8e6e3",
                                  "content": "crucis doctor --workspace . --json",
                                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                                  "fontFamily": "JetBrains Mono",
                                  "fontSize": 12.5,
                                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                                }
                              ]
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "frame",
                          "id": "5DMFW",
                          "name": "subAgentTimeout",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "layout": "vertical",
                          "gap": 8,
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "yf8tS",
                              "name": "sub4h3",
                              "fill": "#2D1F14",
                              "content": "Agent timeout",
                              "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
                              "fontSize": 18,
                              "fontWeight": "600"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "frame",
                              "id": "FHkY5",
                              "name": "codeBlock7",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "fill": "#231A12",
                              "cornerRadius": 10,
                              "padding": [
                                16,
                                20
                              ],
                              "children": [
                                {
                                  "type": "text",
                                  "id": "KCzYq",
                                  "name": "sub4codeText",
                                  "fill": "#e8e6e3",
                                  "content": "Error: Agent timed out after 300s",
                                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                                  "fontFamily": "JetBrains Mono",
                                  "fontSize": 12.5,
                                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                                }
                              ]
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "QKXVE",
                              "name": "sub4p",
                              "fill": "#785E48",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "The default agent timeout is 300 seconds. If your objective is complex or the model is slow, the agent may time out. Crucis treats this as a failed attempt and retries.\n\nTo increase the timeout, pass --timeout to the run command:",
                              "lineHeight": 1.6,
                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                              "fontSize": 14,
                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "frame",
                              "id": "mjjaZ",
                              "name": "codeBlock8",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "fill": "#231A12",
                              "cornerRadius": 10,
                              "padding": [
                                16,
                                20
                              ],
                              "children": [
                                {
                                  "type": "text",
                                  "id": "S0Npt",
                                  "name": "sub4fixText",
                                  "fill": "#e8e6e3",
                                  "content": "crucis run --timeout 600   # 10 minutes",
                                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                                  "fontFamily": "JetBrains Mono",
                                  "fontSize": 12.5,
                                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                                }
                              ]
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "zwmHz",
                              "name": "sub4tips",
                              "fill": "#785E48",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "Other options to reduce timeouts:\n• Simplify the objective (fewer train evals, simpler constraints)\n• Use a faster model via config\n• Reduce max_budget_usd to limit agent thinking time",
                              "lineHeight": 1.6,
                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                              "fontSize": 14,
                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "Ai1Of",
                      "name": "sectionDocker",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "layout": "vertical",
                      "gap": 12,
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "frame",
                          "id": "iYLiF",
                          "name": "h2Wrapper",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "gap": 8,
                          "alignItems": "center",
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "type": "icon_font",
                              "id": "cqaaA",
                              "name": "h2Icon3",
                              "width": 20,
                              "height": 20,
                              "iconFontName": "box",
                              "iconFontFamily": "lucide",
                              "fill": "#785E48"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "DWpOp",
                              "name": "sec3h2",
                              "fill": "#2D1F14",
                              "content": "Docker / Sandbox Issues",
                              "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
                              "fontSize": 23,
                              "fontWeight": "600"
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "frame",
                          "id": "FcnXu",
                          "name": "subDockerNotAvail",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "layout": "vertical",
                          "gap": 8,
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "UrnGl",
                              "name": "sub5h3",
                              "fill": "#2D1F14",
                              "content": "Docker not available",
                              "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
                              "fontSize": 18,
                              "fontWeight": "600"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "frame",
                              "id": "iHUyS",
                              "name": "codeBlock9",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "fill": "#231A12",
                              "cornerRadius": 10,
                              "padding": [
                                16,
                                20
                              ],
                              "children": [
                                {
                                  "type": "text",
                                  "id": "UEcNb",
                                  "name": "sub5codeText",
                                  "fill": "#e8e6e3",
                                  "content": "Sandbox: Docker unavailable, falling back to host pytest",
                                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                                  "fontFamily": "JetBrains Mono",
                                  "fontSize": 12.5,
                                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                                }
                              ]
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "ghMZh",
                              "name": "sub5p",
                              "fill": "#785E48",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "When running crucis run, Crucis checks for Docker availability via docker info. If Docker is not installed or the daemon is not running, Crucis falls back to running pytest directly on the host.\n\nTo use the Docker sandbox:\n1. Install Docker\n2. Start the Docker daemon\n3. Run without the --no-sandbox flag\n\nTo explicitly skip Docker:\ncrucis run --no-sandbox",
                              "lineHeight": 1.6,
                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                              "fontSize": 14,
                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "frame",
                          "id": "0OasG",
                          "name": "subHostPytest",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "layout": "vertical",
                          "gap": 8,
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "0hbvM",
                              "name": "sub6h3",
                              "fill": "#2D1F14",
                              "content": "Host pytest missing",
                              "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
                              "fontSize": 18,
                              "fontWeight": "600"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "x6GCS",
                              "name": "sub6p",
                              "fill": "#785E48",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "When Docker is unavailable (or --no-sandbox is used), Crucis runs host verification via python -m pytest. If pytest is missing, Crucis now fails fast with a preflight error.\n\nFix by installing pytest into the active environment:",
                              "lineHeight": 1.6,
                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                              "fontSize": 14,
                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "frame",
                              "id": "UR4Fh",
                              "name": "codeBlock10",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "fill": "#231A12",
                              "cornerRadius": 10,
                              "padding": [
                                16,
                                20
                              ],
                              "children": [
                                {
                                  "type": "text",
                                  "id": "ZFicZ",
                                  "name": "sub6fixText",
                                  "fill": "#e8e6e3",
                                  "content": "uv pip install pytest   # or: pip install pytest",
                                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                                  "fontFamily": "JetBrains Mono",
                                  "fontSize": 12.5,
                                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                                }
                              ]
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "pkyoD",
                      "name": "sectionConstraints",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "layout": "vertical",
