                      "name": "verifUsage",
                      "fill": "#785E48",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Use task for multi-task objectives to get per-task failure feedback. Use objective when tasks are tightly coupled.",
