                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "WtH1L",
                      "name": "introPara",
                      "fill": "#785E48",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Crucis includes a background policy optimizer powered by GEPA that improves prompt steering over time. After each fit or evaluate run, Crucis queues an optimization job that scores candidate policies against a baseline using black-box evaluation.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.6,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "b4hvn",
                      "name": "sectionHowItWorks",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "layout": "vertical",
                      "gap": 12,
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "FD77l",
                          "name": "s1h",
                          "fill": "#2D1F14",
                          "content": "How It Works",
                          "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
                          "fontSize": 18,
                          "fontWeight": "600"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "aemwx",
                          "name": "s1p",
                          "fill": "#785E48",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "The optimizer runs as a background process that improves Crucis prompts over time:",
                          "lineHeight": 1.6,
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 14,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "frame",
                          "id": "8jR2t",
                          "name": "numberedList",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "layout": "vertical",
                          "gap": 6,
                          "padding": [
                            0,
                            0,
                            0,
                            8
                          ],
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "gcetG",
                              "name": "s1i1",
                              "fill": "#785E48",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "1. After crucis run completes, an optimization job is queued.",
                              "lineHeight": 1.6,
                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                              "fontSize": 14,
                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "SDkP2",
                              "name": "s1i2",
                              "fill": "#785E48",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "2. A detached worker process picks up the job.",
                              "lineHeight": 1.6,
                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                              "fontSize": 14,
                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "iJZ5X",
                              "name": "s1i3",
                              "fill": "#785E48",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "3. The worker builds examples from the objective and checkpoint.",
                              "lineHeight": 1.6,
                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                              "fontSize": 14,
                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "RWyWX",
                              "name": "s1i4",
                              "fill": "#785E48",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "4. GEPA generates candidate policies (prompt directives for generation, adversary, and evaluation agents).",
                              "lineHeight": 1.6,
                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                              "fontSize": 14,
                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "rD07N",
                              "name": "s1i5",
                              "fill": "#785E48",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "5. Each candidate is scored by running the evaluation step in an isolated workspace.",
                              "lineHeight": 1.6,
                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                              "fontSize": 14,
                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "In8v4",
                              "name": "s1i6",
                              "fill": "#785E48",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "6. If the candidate beats the baseline by min_score_delta, it's marked ready for promotion.",
                              "lineHeight": 1.6,
                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                              "fontSize": 14,
                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "yeusD",
                      "name": "sectionPolicyStructure",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "layout": "vertical",
